# mnemosynec.ai · Homepage Draft · BP081

This is the proposed homepage content for mnemosynec.ai. Knight integrates into the Hugo Cephas homepage source at next SHIP cycle. Voice is Founder-direct. Anchors are canonical (Caithedral spelling, canonical numbers strict, three-currency closed loop).

